==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*σῶμα / sōma / so'-mah
From [[σῴζω]]; the body (as a sound whole), used in a very wide application, literally or figuratively:

===Noun===
'''σῶμα'''

# bodily, [[body]], [[slave]].

